item.title: Help me plz
item.dc:creator: @93dcthugs93 93dcthugs93
item.description:
@93dcthugs93 wrote:

Change your character rights to 2, Make sure you save & compile. Also make sure you add yourself to the administrators list in the data folder.

If your using a source like… Phonescape, go into client.Java > Hit CTRL+H. In the ‘Find What’ box type ‘Phonecheck’. In the ‘Replace With’ box type your account name. Hit ‘Replace All’

This is just an example, put the previous owners name in place of Phonecheck’s.
